'''Curse Academy''' is a North American team that has qualified for the [[Riot League Championship Series/North America/2015 Season/Spring Season|2015 Spring NA LCS]]. They will compete under the name {{bl|Gravity (North American Team)|Gravity}}.

== History ==
=== 2015 Preseason ===
Curse Academy were given a seed into the [[Riot League Championship Series/North America/2015 Season/Spring Expansion|Spring Expansion tournament]] as a result of their participation in the Promotion Tournament. With a roster of [[Hauntzer]], [[Saintvicious]], [[Keane]], [[Cop]], and [[Bunny FuFuu]], they beat [[compLexity.White]] 2-0 in the online stage and then advanced to the live tournament, where they defeated [[Coast]] 3-1 and then [[Team Fusion]] 3-1, qualifying for the [[Riot League Championship Series/North America/2015 Season/Spring Season|spring season]]. However, due to the one-team-per-organization rule, they will have to be sold to a new organization.

